<node CREATED="1395308304031" ID="ID_197131209" MODIFIED="1395509621319" POSITION="left" TEXT="Intro">
<richcontent TYPE="NOTE"><html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p charset="utf-8" style="border-left-style: none; text-align: start; border-top-width: 0px; border-top-style: none; letter-spacing: normal; padding-left: 0px; margin-bottom: 0; border-bottom-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 0px; white-space: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 16px; margin-top: 0px; font-size: 12px; border-right-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; text-transform: none; border-right-style: none; padding-bottom: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant: normal; padding-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); border-left-width: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-style: normal; border-bottom-style: none">
      The revelations of Edward snowden has shown how deep the states are stooping to get hold of your data, People who did not care how your data is stored online in your Saas applications are now asking questions, and tough ones. The talk will be about what to do to protect your data from Govt and in that make the application less easy to hack for other people as well.
    </p>
    <h1 style="border-left-style: none; text-align: start; border-top-width: 0px; border-top-style: none; letter-spacing: normal; padding-left: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 0px; white-space: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 16px; margin-top: 0px; font-size: 12px; border-right-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; text-transform: none; border-right-style: none; padding-bottom: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant: normal; padding-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); border-left-width: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-style: normal; border-bottom-style: none">
      The structure of the talk is following
    </h1>
    <ul style="border-left-style: none; text-align: start; border-top-width: 0px; border-top-style: none; letter-spacing: normal; padding-left: 0px; margin-bottom: 0; border-bottom-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 0px; white-space: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 16px; margin-top: 0px; font-size: 12px; border-right-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; text-transform: none; border-right-style: none; padding-bottom: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant: normal; list-style: disc inside; padding-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); border-left-width: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-style: normal; border-bottom-style: none">
      <li style="border-left-style: none; border-top-width: 0px; border-top-style: none; padding-left: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: normal; line-height: inherit; margin-top: 0px; font-size: 12px; border-right-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; border-right-style: none; padding-bottom: 0px; font-variant: inherit; padding-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; border-bottom-style: none">
        How the current default rails setup on the cloud is not enough.
      </li>
      <li style="border-left-style: none; border-top-width: 0px; border-top-style: none; padding-left: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: normal; line-height: inherit; margin-top: 0px; font-size: 12px; border-right-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; border-right-style: none; padding-bottom: 0px; font-variant: inherit; padding-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; border-bottom-style: none">
        Why is it important?
      </li>
      <li style="border-left-style: none; border-top-width: 0px; border-top-style: none; padding-left: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: normal; line-height: inherit; margin-top: 0px; font-size: 12px; border-right-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; border-right-style: none; padding-bottom: 0px; font-variant: inherit; padding-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; border-bottom-style: none">
        How to secure the shell of the application
      </li>
      <li style="border-left-style: none; border-top-width: 0px; border-top-style: none; padding-left: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: normal; line-height: inherit; margin-top: 0px; font-size: 12px; border-right-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; border-right-style: none; padding-bottom: 0px; font-variant: inherit; padding-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; border-bottom-style: none">
        Why just securing the shell of the application
      </li>
      <li style="border-left-style: none; border-top-width: 0px; border-top-style: none; padding-left: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: normal; line-height: inherit; margin-top: 0px; font-size: 12px; border-right-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; border-right-style: none; padding-bottom: 0px; font-variant: inherit; padding-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; border-bottom-style: none">
        Auditing things that might be leaking information that other people

        <ul style="border-left-style: none; border-top-width: 0px; border-top-style: none; padding-left: 0px; margin-bottom: 0; border-bottom-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: normal; line-height: inherit; margin-top: 0px; font-size: 12px; border-right-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; border-right-style: none; padding-bottom: 0px; font-variant: inherit; list-style: disc inside; padding-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; border-bottom-style: none">
          <li style="border-left-style: none; border-top-width: 0px; border-top-style: none; padding-left: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: normal; line-height: inherit; margin-top: 0px; font-size: 12px; border-right-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; border-right-style: none; padding-bottom: 0px; font-variant: inherit; padding-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; border-bottom-style: none">
            Mysql databases/ Third part calls/ Insecure gems/ Insecure filesystems
          </li>
        </ul>
      </li>
      <li style="border-left-style: none; border-top-width: 0px; border-top-style: none; padding-left: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: normal; line-height: inherit; margin-top: 0px; font-size: 12px; border-right-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; border-right-style: none; padding-bottom: 0px; font-variant: inherit; padding-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; border-bottom-style: none">
        Infrastructure choices. Where to host, what to look for in hosting providers.
      </li>
      <li style="border-left-style: none; border-top-width: 0px; border-top-style: none; padding-left: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: normal; line-height: inherit; margin-top: 0px; font-size: 12px; border-right-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; border-right-style: none; padding-bottom: 0px; font-variant: inherit; padding-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; border-bottom-style: none">
        How to implement a system that provides a push button&#160;<font face="inherit" size="12px"><em style="border-left-style: none; border-top-width: 0px; border-top-style: none; padding-left: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: normal; line-height: inherit; margin-top: 0px; font-size: 12px; border-right-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; border-right-style: none; padding-bottom: 0px; font-variant: inherit; padding-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; font-style: italic; font-family: inherit; border-bottom-style: none"><i>secure me</i></em></font>&#160;plan.
      </li>
      <li style="border-left-style: none; border-top-width: 0px; border-top-style: none; padding-left: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: normal; line-height: inherit; margin-top: 0px; font-size: 12px; border-right-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; border-right-style: none; padding-bottom: 0px; font-variant: inherit; padding-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; border-bottom-style: none">
        Caveats and Fine print.
      </li>
    </ul>
    <h1 style="border-left-style: none; text-align: start; border-top-width: 0px; border-top-style: none; letter-spacing: normal; padding-left: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 0px; white-space: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 16px; margin-top: 0px; font-size: 12px; border-right-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; text-transform: none; border-right-style: none; padding-bottom: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant: normal; padding-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); border-left-width: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-style: normal; border-bottom-style: none">
      What this is not
    </h1>
    <ul style="border-left-style: none; text-align: start; border-top-width: 0px; border-top-style: none; letter-spacing: normal; padding-left: 0px; margin-bottom: 0; border-bottom-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 0px; white-space: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 16px; margin-top: 0px; font-size: 12px; border-right-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; text-transform: none; border-right-style: none; padding-bottom: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant: normal; list-style: disc inside; padding-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); border-left-width: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-style: normal; border-bottom-style: none">
      <li style="border-left-style: none; border-top-width: 0px; border-top-style: none; padding-left: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: normal; line-height: inherit; margin-top: 0px; font-size: 12px; border-right-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; border-right-style: none; padding-bottom: 0px; font-variant: inherit; padding-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; border-bottom-style: none">
        I am not talking about making the application hack proof( there will be some authentication security stuff)
      </li>
      <li style="border-left-style: none; border-top-width: 0px; border-top-style: none; padding-left: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: normal; line-height: inherit; margin-top: 0px; font-size: 12px; border-right-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; border-right-style: none; padding-bottom: 0px; font-variant: inherit; padding-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; border-bottom-style: none">
        I am not talking about running a security audit of the application( there will some of the how to audit bit)
      </li>
      <li style="border-left-style: none; border-top-width: 0px; border-top-style: none; padding-left: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: normal; line-height: inherit; margin-top: 0px; font-size: 12px; border-right-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; border-right-style: none; padding-bottom: 0px; font-variant: inherit; padding-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; border-bottom-style: none">
        I am not talking about cryptography and Security fundamentals
      </li>
    </ul>
  </body>
